{"tid":2341043,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"四太梁安琪催何猷君追B 奚夢瑤拒變生仔機器：生多一點聽起來像豬","createTime":"2020-12-26T04:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T03:56:15.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":67,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"09c0ec6d7ed1baca9c94a0bd221b7b35643448cc","tid":2341043,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:37:08.000Z","msg":"賭王何鴻燊四房兒子何猷君去年和大陸模特兒奚夢瑤奉子成婚，為何家誕下男孫何廣燊，亦讓今年去世的賭王在有生之年抱到第一個男孫。二人近月拍攝大陸真人騷節目，公開呈現夫婦日常生活，當中討論到生第二胎的話題，何猷君自爆媽咪梁安琪渴望他們盡早生多幾個小朋友，奚夢瑤聽到笑了幾聲，隨即再說：「生多一點聽起來像豬，老公。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201226/5MHQQC3DJVHNLFWUZMPQ5EKPCM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201226%2F5MHQQC3DJVHNLFWUZMPQ5EKPCM%2F&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUhAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=ca567a35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201226%2F5MHQQC3DJVHNLFWUZMPQ5EKPCM%2F&h=9e173d40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201226/5MHQQC3DJVHNLFWUZMPQ5EKPCM/</a>"},{"pid":"710356ee8d06e2f47e98e280cfe573be3000cd7b","tid":2341043,"uid":365529,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:38:04.000Z","msg":"唔洗啦 黨好快同你哋埋單"},{"pid":"6b5d0276da50d8706a5b1a8a64c4bd63783cbbb1","tid":2341043,"uid":7452,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T05:41:29.000Z","msg":"支那豬"},{"pid":"a8bd41cc8fcb807aac19bb23a62a0a9d9cde7f2b","tid":2341043,"uid":252678,"like":161,"dislike":0,"score":161,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T05:54:03.000Z","msg":"呢個咪就係你生存嘅作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d27a0008f2894e3fbb278710fafed927abf3a0e","tid":2341043,"uid":10726,"like":49,"dislike":2,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T06:03:16.000Z","msg":"個孫可以用阿爺個名嘅咩?<br />\n大不敬啵<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得賭王好快屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd75c5c80c34fff9